Title: Fashion Week
Description:
Ah, the Trial of Style is upon us, $c. 

The outfits, the creativity, the elegance of the Trial are truly a sight to see.

Speak to Primo, the Trial of Style Envoy, in Stormwind to learn more about the event.

A word of warning, Primo can be... challenging to deal with.
ObjectivesText: Speak to a Trial of Style Envoy.
